Tremor turned hearing the screams.  "Oh crud, I forgot 
Slugsligner." he said.  "Looking to the three nebulans on him, he 
ordered them inside him.  He then turned his tank body around 
firing a blast of his cannon at Grimlock.  Then transforming and 
running for the crippled body of Slugslinger.   

"Umm Apeface, minor change in plans, seems Sluggy is almost 
dead, and I am now running bravely to rescue him where I will also 
be destroyed possibly. Over" he said as he once again entered the 
clearing heading for Slugslingers body.
-------------------------------------------------------
JetV was following Tremor then saw him turn.  "What is he doing?" 
he thought to himself, looking at Artemis.

OOC: Airly, the D.E.D members that were at the Autobot ship are 
still really close to there.
